Package: ggsegLobes
Title: Lobar Parcellation Atlas for the 'ggsegverse' Ecosystem
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Giuseppe", "Barisano",
           email = "barisano@stanford.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5598-1369"))
Description: Lobar cortical parcellation (frontal, parietal, temporal,
    occipital, insula, per hemisphere) derived from the Desikan-Killiany
    atlas by dissolving its cortical regions into lobes. Provided as a
    'ggseg_atlas' object for use with 'ggseg'.
